TI  - JTF-SqueezeNet: A SqueezeNet network based on joint time-frequency data representation for egg-laying detection in individually caged ducks
AU  - Lv, Siting
AU  - Mao, Yuanyang
AU  - Liu, Youfu
AU  - Huang, Yigui
