TI  - Remote sensing and GIS-based study of land use/cover dynamics, driving factors, and implications in southern Ethiopia, with special reference to the Legabora watershed
AU  - Mariye, Mehari
AU  - Jianhua, Li
AU  - Maryo, Melesse
AU  - Tsegaye, Gedion
AU  - Aletaye, Eskedar
